We’re going to be unstoppable…

It’s been a tough journey to get to this point, a lot of being told I will never achieve the things I want to, that my dreams are impossible…

I’m doing this for my younger self, still chasing the dreams she had. I have a lot more to give in this sport and I’m nowhere near finding my limit.

Watch Battle for Glory now to hear more about my road to the Collins Cup…
